            {
               "text": "### America: Mesoamerica (Different Frontiers)\n\nIn the following pages of her work, Winifred Creamer analyzes other studies that, by considering additional factors such as technological systems, redefine and expand the original boundaries of Mesoamerica proposed by Paul Kirchhoff. The map presented in this section illustrates the broader region as described in some of the research reviewed by Creamer",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "2d720f02-051c-4469-b425-7d020f2c2f9b",
